Description: GodsApp — security auditing & research suite
 GodsApp is a native GTK4 desktop application providing a unified interface
 for reconnaissance, web app testing, network analysis, password auditing,
 exploitation tooling, OSINT, forensics, and more. Tools run as managed
 subprocesses with live output, structured findings, and a tamper-evident
 evidence locker.
